# Productized Services Ideas

> Pre-packaged, fixed-price service offerings that create recurring revenue from consulting expertise.

---

## Why Productized Services?

**The Problem with Traditional Consulting:**
- Feast-or-famine revenue cycles
- Every project requires custom scoping
- Trading time for money with no leverage
- Unpredictable cash flow

**The Productized Solution:**
> "Productization is about identifying the 20% of your services that solve 80% of your clients' problems, then creating systematic ways to deliver those solutions at scale."

> Source: [Consulting Success](https://www.consultingsuccess.com/consultants-guide-to-productization)

**Real Results:**
- Mike Gammarino: From feast-or-famine to predictable monthly revenue
- Doug Nelson: Closed $55K and $33.5K projects within 3 days of productizing
- One practitioner: Hit $10K/month ($120K/year) in recurring revenue with Facebook Ads productized service

> Source: [Coveted Consultant](https://covetedconsultant.com/productized-service-examples/)

---

## Idea 1: Website Care Plans

**Market Context:** Website maintenance is a proven recurring revenue opportunity. After building a site, ongoing maintenance is essential - and most businesses neglect it.

> Source: [MarTech](https://martech.org/how-seo-agencies-can-earn-recurring-revenue-with-site-management-services/)

### Service Tiers

| Tier | Price | Includes |
|------|-------|----------|
| **Essential** | $99/mo | Security updates, backups, uptime monitoring, 30min support |
| **Growth** | $249/mo | Above + 2hrs dev time, SEO monitoring, monthly report |
| **Premium** | $499/mo | Above + 5hrs dev time, content updates, priority support |

### Viability Assessment

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High |
| Effort | Low (systematize existing skills) |
| Revenue | $10K-30K/yr per 20-50 clients |
| Moat | Relationships + quality |

### Target Clients

**Best Fit:**
- Past ndev Consulting clients (natural upsell)
- Small businesses with WordPress/React sites
- Companies with no in-house developer
- Agencies needing overflow capacity

**Acquisition Strategy:**
1. Offer to every past client
2. Include in new project proposals
3. Partner with designers who don't maintain
4. Local business outreach

### Operations

**Tools Required:**
- ManageWP or MainWP (WordPress management)
- UptimeRobot (monitoring)
- BackupBuddy or similar
- Freshdesk/Zendesk (simple ticketing)
- Stripe (recurring billing)

**Time Investment:**
- Essential tier: ~30min/client/month average
- Growth tier: ~3hrs/client/month
- Premium tier: ~6hrs/client/month

**At 20 clients on Essential ($99):** $1,980/mo, ~10 hours/mo = $198/hr effective

