## Idea 3: Technical SEO Audit Package

**Market Context:** Local SEO services range from $300-2,000/month. Technical audits are a proven entry point.

> Source: [SERPS](https://serps.com/blog/local-seo-costs/)

### Service Definition

**Fixed Deliverable:** Comprehensive technical SEO audit with prioritized action plan

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| Price | $997 one-time |
| Timeline | 1 week |
| Deliverable | 20-30 page report with prioritized fixes |

### What's Included

1. **Technical Analysis**
   - Site speed audit (Core Web Vitals)
   - Mobile usability review
   - Crawlability assessment
   - Schema markup audit
   - Security (HTTPS, mixed content)

2. **Content Analysis**
   - Title/meta optimization opportunities
   - Heading structure review
   - Internal linking analysis
   - Content gap identification

3. **Competitive Benchmarking**
   - Top 3 competitor comparison
   - Keyword opportunity analysis
   - Backlink profile comparison

4. **Action Plan**
   - Prioritized fix list (high/medium/low impact)
   - Estimated effort for each fix
   - DIY instructions vs "hire us" options

### Upsell Path

Audit → Monthly SEO Retainer ($500-2,000/mo)

### Viability Assessment

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High |
| Effort | Low (can systematize with tools) |
| Revenue | $15K-30K/yr at 15-30 audits |
| Moat | Quality of analysis + actionability |

